      "text": "<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?> <rss version=\"2.0\" xmlns:atom=\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\"><channel><title>Python.org Jobs Feed</title><link>https://www.python.org/jobs/</link><description>Python jobs from Python.org</description><atom:link href=\"https://www.python.org/jobs/feed/rss/\" rel=\"self\"/><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:47:21 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>DevOps Engineer-FULLY REMOTE-US, CANADA, EUROPE based only, ActivePrime, Inc.</title><link>https://www.python.org/jobs/8061/</link><description>REMOTE, REMOTE &lt;p&gt;THIS IS A FULLY REMOTE ROLE -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;YOU MUST BE LOCATED EITHER IN THE US, CANADA or WESTERN EUROPE&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;We're seeking a versatile DevOps Engineer to help scale our infrastructure and operations.",
