    {
      "charEnd": 6019,
      "charStart": 4613,
      "factId": "hz.web.22178ee56446ef42.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "To give you an idea of the kind of projects you’ll get to work on, here are some examples of our impact.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;We’ve helped:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul class=\"simple\"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://opendataservices.coop/case-studies/making-sense-of-what-development-and-humanitarian-data-enables-in-practice/\"&gt;improve how development and humanitarian resources are tracked&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://opendataservices.coop/case-studies/tracking-infrastructure-sustainability/\"&gt;understand the sustainability of infrastructure projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://opendataservices.coop/case-studies/climate-disaster-risk-open-standard/\"&gt;build standards that climate and disaster risk data easier to find&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://opendataservices.coop/case-studies/mapping-high-speed-internet/\"&gt;map high-speed internet networks to close connectivity gaps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://opendataservices.coop/case-studies/charitable-donations-data-publishing/\"&gt;build data infrastructure that makes grantmaking more informed and effective&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;We recognise there are many paths to becoming a software developer.",
